        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【酱油吃多了，皮肤会变黑？？[费解][裂开]】不会！酱油以及醋里的黑色是焦糖色素，和我们皮肤里的黑色素，无论是来源，还是结构都没有任何相似性。[老师好]酱油...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【酱油吃多了，皮肤会变黑？？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<br><br>不会！酱油以及醋里的黑色是焦糖色素，和我们皮肤里的黑色素，无论是来源，还是结构都没有任何相似性。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[老师好]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/0d/2022_Teacher_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>酱油中含有的酪氨酸是合成黑色素不可少的氨基酸，但焦糖色素及酪氨酸吃到肚子里，会被消化道的消化液（主要是胃酸）分解掉，所以，根本不用担心酱油吃多会沉积到皮肤里面。<br><br>皮肤变黑的两个主要因素是遗传和日晒，<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>阿卫提醒，坚持做好防晒，才是预防皮肤变黑最有效的方式！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>🌚<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjns2dhofej20u00u0abk.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjns2dia0ij20nu0u0q8k.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
